          "name": "Hover",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "Combat transports have a series of six large clockwork fans built into their flat under body. These fans can be activated when Stopping the vehicle to allow it to hover within 5 feet of the surface so that troops can be quickly deployed via forward and aft ramps, regardless of the nature of the terrain.",
